            <abstract>
                <p>Miracle on the Egyptian sailors whose boat was troubled by a strong wind. This miracle is transmitted in the section for 
                    Ḫǝdār in the <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1295Dersan">Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel</ref> witness <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet82">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 82</ref>, but in the section for Ḥamle in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet121">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 121</ref></p>
